{"tid":2111147,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【美國大選】拜登引《毛語錄》惹網民嘩然","createTime":"2020-07-16T10:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T14:00:50.000Z","uid":343294,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4f7332c758bde4d957ddb182bfa565f256319f00","tid":2111147,"uid":343294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:49:51.000Z","msg":"美國總統參選人拜登（Joe Biden）引用《毛語錄》語句「婦女能頂半邊天」，令美國網民嘩然。<br />\n《霍士新聞》引述《大西洋月刊》作家的多維爾（Edward-Isaac Dovere）報道，拜登在一場網上籌款活動的問答環節中，指「必須把真正的經濟援助送到女性手中」，接著說出《毛語錄》語句「婦女能頂半邊天」（women hold up half the sky），因而遭美國網友在社交網站Twitter 嘲諷為「中國喬」（China Joe）和北京拜登（Beijing Biden），戲稱他「跟習近平有一樣的崇拜對象」、「根本是共產黨員」。<br />\n<br />\n在1955年，貴州民主婦女聯合會刊發了一篇叫做《在合作社內實行男女同酬》的文章，內容表揚首個實行男女同工同酬的村落，毛澤東看到文章後批示各鄉社仿效，其後提出口號「婦女能頂半邊天」，並將其收錄到《毛語錄》。<br />\n據內地媒體報道，美國國會圖書館的官方網站曾以「婦女能頂半邊天」為標題，介紹中國女性地位變遷的書籍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2697066\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2697066&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaYgDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=74b43afb\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2697066</a>"},{"pid":"a5bb9985095e0a2b243b3a31b0c3ed45dc02484f","tid":2111147,"uid":511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"露底了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde2461fb6f315217881c16af25cbef90b24b856","tid":2111147,"uid":178875,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:53:45.000Z","msg":"唔好傻啦<br />\n拜登贏硬 trump咁廢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ae297a84a17a471d8360d04490c9d17cf384c8","tid":2111147,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:54:37.000Z","msg":"民望高過 trump 有啲不耐煩？"},{"pid":"b750dae30017f0a6f39810cfd5b1a488679a953e","tid":2111147,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:56:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f4a1f2363c2eba59825b0b4ba228